<link>https://the-decoder.com/openais-new-prompting-guide-tells-users-to-stop-overthinking-and-start-with-the-result/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://the-decoder.com/?p=37745</guid>
<pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 17:47:39 +0000</pubDate>
<source>the-decoder.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【the-decoder.com】OpenAI发布了一份面向普通用户而非开发者的提示指南。该指南摒弃了僵化的公式，提出了四个可选构建模块：目标、背景、格式和约束。核心建议很简单：描述你想要的结果，而非达成结果的步骤。这是OpenAI首次在单一框架中涵盖Chat和Codex。本文《OpenAI新提示指南：告诉用户停止过度思考，从结果出发》最初发表于The Decoder。<br/><br/><a href="https://the-decoder.com/openais-new-prompting-guide-tells-users-to-stop-overthinking-and-start-with-the-result/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
